2. Ra2 Rg8 3. Kh1 Rg7 4. Bf3 Rag8 5. Rg2 Rxg2 6. Bxg2 a5 7. Kg1 h4 8. Kf1 Ng4
9. h3 Nf6 10. Kf2 Rg3 11. c5 Ne4+
