1... Kg8 2. Rfd2 Qe7 3. c5 dxc5 4. Rd7 Qe6 5. Bf1
{ An awesome way to bring everyone together. Black can't cope with all the threats at the same time. }
5... cxb4 6. axb4 Bf7 7. Rxf7 Rxf7 8. Bc4 Qg6+ 9. Rg2 *


