dxc4 4. Bxg7+ Kxg7 5. Qb2+ Qf6 6. Qxb7+ Rf7 7. Qxe4
{ You only really needed to see up to here but since Payen did not convert this position, I thought I would provide a sample line for White to win as fast as possible. }
7... Qxf2+ 8. Kh1 Qe2 9. Qd4+
