[FEN "2rrb1k1/1pp1q1pp/2n5/3p1p2/1P1Pn3/5NP1/2Q1PPBP/2RRB1K1 w - - 0 1"]
[SetUp "1"]

1. b5
{ Black would dream of playing c5 by moving his knight away but White denies him his only plan. }
1... Na7 2. b6
